=== post_it plugin 0.0.1

This is a post_it plugin for Chiliproject.

ONLY compatible with Chiliproject 3.X NOT compatible with Chiliproject 2.X


== Getting the plugin

The newest version is always at {GitHub}[http://github.com/kwanko/chiliproject_post_it].


=== Feature

1. Create a note and display it like a post it on the screen

2. Note can be sent to another user

3. Note can be created with alert which will occur at the setting time


=== Plugin installation

1. Copy the plugin directory(chiliproject_post_it) into the vendor/plugins directory
   NOTE: The plugin directory must be chiliproject_post_it!

2. Migrate plugin:
   rake db:migrate_plugins NAME=chiliproject_post_it RAILS_ENV=production

3. Start Chiliproject


